{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story02","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Mikura","narration":"Having become curious about that hokora on the hill,@I went to research it at the libarry.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"There, a thought went through my mind..."},{"autoTurnLast":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":101,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"nameCenter":"Mikura","textCenter":"This hill...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"Looks just like a kofun, right?"},{"autoTurnLast":1,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textCenter":"Next up, a bibliographic survey.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textCenter":"I can hardly imagine that it's actually an@undiscovered kofun, but whatever the case..."},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":100}],"textCenter":"I want to start by digging up everything I can@about the hilltop hokora!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(The majority of the literature cited...)"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(Appears to be in the possession of Kamihama@University's library.)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303801,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"Guess I'll head to the university first."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Temari","textCenter":".......","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800800,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"id":303801}],"nameLeft":"Mikura","textLeft":"Hello, ma'am.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800800}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Why, Komachi-san! Hello to you too, dear."},{"chara":[{"id":800800}],"textRight":"You're here to see the manuscripts you checked@out, right? I'll show you where they are."},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textLeft":"Thank you very much."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800800,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":800800}],"textRight":"Here's the key.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800800}],"textRight":"I take it you know how to view microfilm?"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Yes, I'm quite familiar."},{"chara":[{"id":800800}],"textRight":"Such expertise for a high-school student!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800800}],"textRight":"Ah, if only our college kids here were as@passionate as you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303801}],"textLeft":"*Chuckle*..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800800}],"textRight":"Well, knock yourself out!@If you have any questions, give me a call."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Thanks again!"},{"autoTurnLast":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Mikura","narration":"It was tough going--@I could hardly identify some of the script,@let alone translate it...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"But I managed to find one single passage@that clearly described the hokora."},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Mikura","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"(Finally...!)"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(This indicates that the hokora was around since@the Muromachi period!)"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(And even at that time, it was apparently pretty@old already.)"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"textCenter":"(Well, that said...)"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(This has zero to do with whether or not the@hill is a kofun.)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(But knowing that it was revered since ancient@times is plenty exciting on its own!)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303801}],"textCenter":"Let's see, now."},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"The next thing we ought to investigate is@whether they've found any artifacts nearby..."},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textCenter":"Haniwa fragments, for instance!"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
